reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 26, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Absolutely wonderful product
reviews.reviewText: I have scleroderma and have developed a reaction to regular commercial toothpastes and mouthwashes. I don't know what the ingredient is that's irritating me, but I do know it's not fluoride because I can tolerate Tom's toothpaste just fine.For five years I've been hunting for an alternative to the regular stuff and it's all crappy. Nothing seems to leave me feeling fresh and they don't work. I've been struggling with staining, yeast and bacterial overgrowth, and plaque since I switched. This mouthwash combined with one toothpaste makes the perfect combination. I used this mouthwash in the first afternoon that I got it and again before bed. By morning the chronic yeast problem on my tongue was gone! Over the last week I don't have anymore new staining. (Now I just have to get the old stuff removed)At almost $10, it's a little pricey, but not so much that I can't manage it. Totally worth it! Tastes really good, burns a little but not horrible, and actually WORKS!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 25, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My Teeth Feel Squeaky Clean
reviews.reviewText: I had this item in my wishlist for months, because I find things that look interesting and useful. I finally purchased this item and my teeth have never been happier. My teeth actually told me that after the first time I used it, "Derek, thank you. We've never been happier. You can never use another mouthwash because if you do, we'll hurt you." At first, I thought I was hallucinating. It turns out, I was.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: It mouthwash was okay, but I was truly expecting a cleaner feeling for the price. I feel it's overpriced. I think I got caught up in the aesthetics of the bottle. As it is really cute, but the mouthwash is nothing special.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Little Pricey but Good Quality
reviews.reviewText: While this mouthwash was expensive, the flavor was fabulous! I've used all the mouthwash, and I'm actually reusing the bottle to store my other mouthwash. I'm sad to say this brand didn't tackle my "coffee breath" the way I had hoped, but it was very pleasant overall. If you need a decent mouthwash and don't require something with more strength, I definitely recommend it.

reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. The bottle's aesthetics look wonderful and would of matched my minimalist bathroom, however this is what I received. Sellers has not address anything to me. Buyer beware!!
